Package: LoCoHverlap
Type: Package
Title: Estimate animal range overlap using LoCoh and EMD
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Brian J.", "Smith", 
    email = "bjsmith@aggiemail.usu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Streamlines the workflow of estimating animal range overlap.
    First fits Local Convex Hulls (LoCoHs) to the animal location data. Then 
    converts each LoCoH to a utilization distribution (UD). Finally, estimates
    overlap using Earth Mover's Distance (EMD).
